org.openadaptor.auxil.expression
Interface IPostfixFunction

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractFunction, BinaryOp, UnaryOperation
public interface IPostfixFunction

Interface for PostFix functions (which are used by expressions).

Implementing classes should be able to perform postfix operations using operands from a (supplied) stack. The resulting value will be available on the top of the stack.

Author:
Eddy Higgins
